primaryText.text: But in reality, mice prefer grains, fruits, and manmade foods that are high in sugar, and tend to turn up their noses at very smelly foods, like cheese. In fact, a 2006 study found that mice actively avoid cheese and dairy in general.

primaryText.text: Parmesan cheese is made from unpasteurized milk. It has a hard, gritty texture, and is fruity and nutty in taste.

bodyTemplate2Data.hintText: Try, "Alexa, give me a fact about cheese"

primaryText.text: Mild Gouda is a semi hard cheese with a creamy texture and mild nutty flavor. Easy to cut and grate, it also melts beautifully. Gouda is a Dutch yellow cheese made from cow's milk, and one of the most popular cheeses worldwide.
